snippet.textDisplay: I'm going to add an image link here--it's something I posted while chatting with the guys making Crisis VRigage--because I REALLY don't want to see the same issue in Half-Life: Alyx on Rift that I've now seen in a few VR games on Rift (Crisis VRigade and Robo Recall are a couple that immediately come to mind): https://ibb.co/pQR4yq6 So please keep it in mind, any Valve employees who might be viewing this video. It is basically a deal-breaker for me if you can't get this particular aspect of the control and aiming right, so if you can't--and I would be stunned and very disappointed if you actually can't--then please at least add an option to let me adjust the angle of the gun myself so I can actually set it to the correct angle manually. Thank you.
snippet.textOriginal: I'm going to add an image link here--it's something I posted while chatting with the guys making Crisis VRigage--because I REALLY don't want to see the same issue in Half-Life: Alyx on Rift that I've now seen in a few VR games on Rift (Crisis VRigade and Robo Recall are a couple that immediately come to mind): https://ibb.co/pQR4yq6 So please keep it in mind, any Valve employees who might be viewing this video. It is basically a deal-breaker for me if you can't get this particular aspect of the control and aiming right, so if you can't--and I would be stunned and very disappointed if you actually can't--then please at least add an option to let me adjust the angle of the gun myself so I can actually set it to the correct angle manually. Thank you.
